Dialogue: 0,0:00:-14.00,0:00:-06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Horo-horo-horo-horo-horo...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.35,0:00:06.74,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.76,0:00:08.85,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.87,0:00:16.87,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.24,0:00:26.54,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We've left the established course
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.56,0:00:29.96,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we're rowing straight toward
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.98,0:00:35.50,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,The borderline between the sky and the ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.52,0:00:41.72,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,In the dark depths of the ocean,\Nadventure holds its breath
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.74,0:00:48.73,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have a good time just imagining it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.75,0:00:53.23,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.25,0:00:55.31,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.33,0:01:03.33,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.58,0:01:13.01,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,"That feeling" I get when embarking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.03,0:01:16.21,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something I hope to remember always
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.23,0:01:21.76,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can, I won't be afraid of anything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.78,0:01:27.97,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,With our pulses racing, let's go on a trip now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.99,0:01:35.02,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Shy hearts engrave the rhythm of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.04,0:01:39.15,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.17,0:01:41.77,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.79,0:01:46.13,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.15,0:01:48.83,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.85,0:01:50.50,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Life is "Adventurous"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.52,0:01:52.21,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Be aware it's "Dangerous"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.23,0:01:53.87,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's gonna be "One of us"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.89,0:01:55.50,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And a trip goes on because
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.52,0:01:57.04,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We da pirate of the "Mass"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.06,0:01:58.96,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,To the West, To the East
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.98,0:02:00.57,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta find my way, Sail away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.59,0:02:01.74,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,All the way to "One piece"!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.76,0:02:06.00,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff a dream into your empty chest
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.02,0:02:08.18,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And spread your wings
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.20,0:02:12.56,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If the wind blowing through\Nthem dyes your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.58,0:02:14.98,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's press forward
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.00,0:02:19.09,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.11,0:02:21.47,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.49,0:02:25.88,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.90,0:02:33.85,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.87,0:02:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time is the \NGreat Pirate Era.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.84,0:02:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Countless pirates fight \Ndesperately for the One Piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.52,0:02:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the great treasure left behind by \NGold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.67,0:02:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body turned \Nto rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.87,0:02:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,also takes to the sea to become \Nthe next King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.54,0:02:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As Luffy and his friends \Novercome numerous adventures,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.39,0:03:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the World Government is less and \Nless able to ignore their existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.24,0:03:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.85,0:03:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of adventure \Nis waiting for us next?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.22,0:03:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The crew, on its way \Nto the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.22,0:03:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will speed along the \NGrand Line again today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.73,0:03:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Separated from the rest of the Straw Hats,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.48,0:03:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy is headed to the Navy Headquarters in order to rescue his brother, Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.83,0:03:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile,  the rest of the Straw Hats are...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.93,0:03:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Friends' Whereabouts! A Huge Tomb and the Panty Debt!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.21,0:03:41.22,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(450,1)}"Gloom Island\NRuins of the Muggy Kingdom"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.24,0:03:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, a short time ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.11,0:03:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro who was forced to stay with Perona was...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.60,0:04:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no good! I got to hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.63,0:04:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did he go?! That stupid swordsman!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.74,0:04:21.15,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(450,1)}"A Few Hours Ago"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.17,0:04:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.17,0:04:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the room that I was sleeping in?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.01,0:04:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this building a maze?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.01,0:04:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.45,0:04:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.28,0:04:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that it'd be fun to use Negative Hollow
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.49,0:05:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to make him depressed when he finds his sword
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.65,0:05:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I told him where his sword was but that was 2 days ago already...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.01,0:05:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He can't find it no matter how many hints I give!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.72,0:05:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why're you here?! You use your Devil Fruit power again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.26,0:05:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?! Don't accuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.77,0:05:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who kept losing your way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.73,0:05:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you climb the stairs behind us, all the hallways lead directly to the room!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.40,0:05:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you get lost?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.97,0:05:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! You're not clear enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.04,0:05:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not my fault at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.71,0:05:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a fantasista, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.92,0:05:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.13,0:05:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you mishear me so badly?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.65,0:05:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't realize you were that pathetic without your sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.26,0:06:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so heartbreaking just to look at you now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.89,0:06:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How sad!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.94,0:06:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You put me in this situation!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.55,0:06:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good things will happen to you someday!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.67,0:06:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.99,0:06:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.06,0:06:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can have it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.68,0:06:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why're you doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.73,0:06:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't mean anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.81,0:06:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you have your sword, you can't attack me because I'm a replica.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.83,0:06:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing can harm this body.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.34,0:06:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So a swordsman like you poses no threat to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.70,0:06:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, I don't want any servants who are not cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.04,0:06:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not giving it back for no reason!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.46,0:06:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I use him, I can go back to Thriller Bark!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.80,0:06:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like he's empty-headed so I can easily handle him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.25,0:06:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use him as I please,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.31,0:07:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,toy with him and leave him on this island at the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.74,0:07:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not so bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.46,0:07:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.58,0:07:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! I let him get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.75,0:07:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did he go?! That stupid swordsman!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.14,0:07:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how Luffy and the others are doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.40,0:07:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I gotta go back to Sabaody Archipelago!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.06,0:07:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope that they're okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.29,0:07:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone focus on escaping!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.14,0:07:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As we are now, we can't beat these guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.26,0:08:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't just stay here doing nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.24,0:08:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.98,0:08:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I know that castle... or not...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.30,0:08:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.03,0:08:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like the other castle! How confusing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.06,0:08:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think so?! I'm sick of your sense of direction!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.95,0:08:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe how nice I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.67,0:08:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have to guide him to the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.24,0:08:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's okay! I'll take advantage of him wisely!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.47,0:08:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the right way?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.46,0:08:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have no right to ask me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.97,0:08:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I checked it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.85,0:08:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just shut up and follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.89,0:08:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.73,0:08:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Augh! What did I just say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.45,0:08:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Oh, it's that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.95,0:09:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's this way, you stupid swordsman!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.32,0:09:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.20,0:09:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't you even follow me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.28,0:09:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to lead the way properly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.75,0:09:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it my fault?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.86,0:09:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's exhausting just staying with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.96,0:09:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.43,0:09:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got tired even though you're flying?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.51,0:09:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! It's your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.22,0:09:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.55,0:09:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind! I'll get sick just by talking to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.39,0:09:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This tree looks familiar!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.40,0:09:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.84,0:09:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.84,0:09:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe somebody else has been sent here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.26,0:09:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I gotta go and check!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.87,0:09:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what're you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.01,0:09:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need a toy like you that is just annoying and boring!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.71,0:10:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wander on this island forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.38,0:10:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it? I want somebody cute this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.94,0:10:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what took you so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.60,0:10:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.26,0:10:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-W-Why are you here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.11,0:10:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? I thought that the sea was this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.96,0:10:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're really a fantasista!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.86,0:10:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.33,0:10:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy's really something... probably?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.23,0:10:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That tree must've been cut down recently!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.36,0:11:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How disappointing! It was just a tree falling down?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.51,0:11:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody has been sent so that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.20,0:11:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I have to settle for him for now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.77,0:11:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I love the depressing atmosphere after a war!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.82,0:11:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so enchanting!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.16,0:11:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe some restless evil spirits did that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.53,0:11:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.68,0:11:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where are you going? Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.84,0:12:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this a...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.99,0:12:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Tomb?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.51,0:12:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who made this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.93,0:12:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has carved out from a big tree. It took great skill!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.40,0:12:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's very big!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.82,0:12:29.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Again! Somebody is here as I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.05,0:12:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.56,0:13:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! It bounced off!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.42,0:13:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.64,0:13:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.61,0:13:49.41,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1)}"Lazy Bones Island\NThe Land of Poverty - Hungeria"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.43,0:13:50.72,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Lazy Bones Island
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.74,0:13:53.90,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,the land of poverty "Hungeria."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.92,0:14:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brook was mistaken as Satan, the king of devils-- by its residents.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.98,0:14:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a clear morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.84,0:14:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.48,0:14:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if they are all looking at the sun like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.23,0:14:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'm sure they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.92,0:14:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because whatever happens, the sun will always rise!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.05,0:14:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if I can stay alive,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.06,0:14:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will see them again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.62,0:14:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, come to think of it, this island is very deserted!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.59,0:14:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I didn't notice yesterday but inside that building,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.84,0:14:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there was an altar and dolls for some kind of rituals,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.34,0:15:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,uncanny tapestries and posters on the wall,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.60,0:15:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and macabre-looking mural decorations.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.77,0:15:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And those things on the floor - are they tools for voodoo or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.41,0:15:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I think about it, it's kind of weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.25,0:15:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you awoken?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.90,0:15:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were just going to visit your room bringing breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.96,0:15:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.12,0:15:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.32,0:15:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How generous you people are! You don't even know me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.46,0:15:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops! I haven't introduced myself yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.46,0:15:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the head of this country Pekkori.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.10,0:15:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pekkori-san! Well then, I gratefully accept the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.40,0:15:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.71,0:16:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could I look at your panties?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.03,0:16:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Panties! Hurry and show him your underwear!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.50,0:16:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no no, um... I don't need to see the guys' underwear!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.17,0:16:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to hesitate! Enjoy it as much as you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.34,0:16:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?! Augh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.86,0:16:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for the big meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.36,0:16:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so full that I can barely move!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.00,0:16:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I don't have a stomach to be full!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.36,0:16:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's our one-week-worth of food!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.01,0:16:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be patient for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.76,0:16:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Satan-sama, did you say that you wanted to ask us a favor?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.87,0:16:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to set sail right away! So I need a ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.69,0:16:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No! Have we done something that made you upset?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.84,0:16:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.46,0:17:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, everybody! Show your underwear for his dessert!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.80,0:17:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough with the underwear! Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.04,0:17:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't like underwear anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.02,0:17:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.68,0:17:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to get back to my friends at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.98,0:17:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get back?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.26,0:17:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.94,0:17:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-At any cost?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.94,0:17:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I feel bad because I've been treated so nicely.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.71,0:17:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're over!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.87,0:17:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If underwear won't do it, there's nothing we can do to keep you here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.94,0:17:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the end of this country!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.64,0:17:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's come to this, we have no choice but to take our lives...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.57,0:17:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-W-Wait a minute! Please relax!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.58,0:17:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.39,0:17:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it seems like you have a story there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.13,0:17:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you call me Satan and...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.25,0:17:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you said something about Longarm Tribe last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.30,0:18:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you tell me about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.89,0:18:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This country has been overrun by the Longarm Tribe for too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.57,0:18:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only money and goods and food...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.32,0:18:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but they also take men and women in their prime from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.25,0:18:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And as you see, our country is devastated
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.31,0:18:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and suffering extreme poverty!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.03,0:18:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, those meal were...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.86,0:18:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm ashamed to say this but we made them from what little food we had.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.17,0:18:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.22,0:18:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to get out of the situation,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.11,0:18:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we kept praying to all the gods and goddesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.97,0:18:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only that but we have invited famous psychics from around the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.59,0:18:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to curse our enemies to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.08,0:18:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But when it didn't work, we resorted to black magic
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.49,0:19:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and finally, we got you, Satan-sama - the king of devils, to be summoned here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.42,0:19:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Satan-sama! You're our one and only hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.88,0:19:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please deal the Longarm Tribe a bloody blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.26,0:19:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--We beg you!\N--We beg you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.85,0:19:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.61,0:19:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Will you please curse them to death for us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.44,0:19:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Satan-sama!\N--Satan-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.11,0:19:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.53,0:19:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Longarm Tribe!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.47,0:19:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.08,0:19:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.71,0:19:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you wanna get hurt?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.45,0:19:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give us back the girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.44,0:19:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit messing with us, jerks!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.59,0:19:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let my daughter go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.43,0:19:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll give you hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.65,0:20:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.86,0:20:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.35,0:20:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, do you see that they're taking the young lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.06,0:20:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.04,0:20:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put a curse on them now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.96,0:20:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I beg you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.37,0:20:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I mean, we got to help her now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.64,0:20:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Satan-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.22,0:20:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-They took her!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.30,0:20:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why weren't they doing anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.17,0:20:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...though someone was taking their friend or family?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.25,0:20:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't they try to fight and take her back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.10,0:20:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Satan-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.78,0:20:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I beg you! Please give them punishment!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.08,0:20:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We beg you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.25,0:20:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're really dependent on other people!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.60,0:20:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that young lady is a victim! She doesn't deserve that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.04,0:21:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! I owe you for the place to stay and all the panties I saw so I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.50,0:21:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.92,0:21:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Satan! Satan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.82,0:21:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Satan! Satan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.68,0:21:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Satan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.22,0:21:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Luffy-san and everybody!"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.33,0:21:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Right now, I'm surrounded by a lot of underwear-- and am being called Satan-sama."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.11,0:21:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm sorry but could you wait a little?"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.79,0:21:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I owe them and if I don't pay them back, it'll spoil my skeleton-hood!"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.26,0:21:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"So give me some time."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.69,0:21:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"As soon as I finish this, I'll get to wherever you are!"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.41,0:21:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been almost an hour since we left Impel down.-- If the wind is right,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.34,0:21:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we should have reached to Navy Headquarters already!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.69,0:22:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't we moving too slowly?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.35,0:22:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna get there after everything has finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.88,0:22:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crocodile!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.07,0:22:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Navy is not the one that will beat Whitebeard! I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.03,0:22:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You still feel that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.78,0:22:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can beat you first if you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.39,0:22:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.22,0:22:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm on my way! Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.64,0:22:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.39,0:23:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy and the others continue\Nsailing on the Tarai Current.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.25,0:23:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't be long before they reach Marineford.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.01,0:23:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy watches the Vivre Card\Nto make sure Ace is still safe,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.81,0:23:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,whiel he reminisces over his past with his brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.52,0:23:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.06,0:23:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A Special Retrospective Before Marineford!\NThe Vow of the Brotherhood!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.73,0:23:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
